short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Getaway Shootout Online is a 2-player shooting game where you have to jump around and kill.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Getaway Shootout is a chaotic race to reach the getaway objective in each map. Race against the computer or grab a friend to prove who is best. Collect power-ups and weapons along the way, and navigate through tough maps. Survive by jumping left and right and using power-ups and weapons to gain an edge over your opponents.

Features

Play solo or together with your friend
Many unlockable characters with unique appearance to play
Lots of power-ups and weapons
Plenty of maps with a different getaway objective
Fun and engaging gameplay
Cool but hard to master physics

Faq

Q: How do I unlock characters in Getaway Shootout?
A: Use the coins you earn in-game to unlock new characters.
Q: How do I play Getaway Shootout?
A: Master the physics by practicing. Collect power-ups to make it easier.
Q: Is Getaway Shootout available on mobile?
A: Getaway shootout can be played in web browser or on iOS.
Q: Who made Getaway Shootout?
A: Getaway Shootout is developed by New Eich Games, a developer that has made a multitude of crazy physics-based games.
